    <comment>I am the author. execdir was originally created by Gustavo Costa in 2022, and I forked it in 2025. I replaced the text-based key-value storage with lmdb and made aliases optional, which improves usability. I also replaced the makefile with a CMakeLists.txt file.</comment>
